  "instructions": [
    "Poach the pine nuts in a mixture of water and sugar until soft, about 5 minutes.",
    "In a saucepan, heat heavy cream with unsalted butter over medium heat until just simmering.",
    "Add floral extract, vanilla bean paste, crushed pine nuts, and rose petals to the cream mixture. Stir well.",
    "Reduce heat and let the mixture simmer for 2-3 minutes or until slightly thickened.",
    "Blend the mixture in a blender if desired to achieve a smooth consistency."
